divs: sighting detailsdriving east on bell road at approximately 3:15pm today (sunday, oct 20, 2009) i saw what looked like the video posted below. at first i thought the large object was a bunch of balloons tied together but as i stared at it, it became clear it was somthing more. upon turning on my computer tonight, i noted google was showing a cartoon ufo so i did a google search of ufo's on news and found this video. it's what i saw today. has anyone else in phoenix reported this? http:\\www.youtube.com\watch?v=yyiysv5auak&feature=player_embedded
